Summary: I got up a little after 1am.
divs: Sighting DetailsI got up a little after 1am, I went out the south side of my house. I looked to the east sky and saw a orange color flame like object coming from the east going west,it came almost right over me just a little south of me, than another in about 30 seconds looked just like the first. Than 4 more close together. than about 30 seconds 1 more than about 30 seconds 1 more. all in all I saw around 20 objects all looked alike all flying in the same flight path, and spaced the same distance from one another other than the 4 that were close together. picture looks like a round ball, but to the unaided eye they looked more cigar shaped
